title: 11/17/21 DPS Best Of
itunes:title: 11/17/21 DPS Best Of
description:
On Today's Dan Patrick Show, DP talks to ESPN Football analyst about which team has better shot to beat Ohio State, Michigan or Michigan State. Sports Business Insider Darren Rovell takes us inside the deal that will change the name of the Staples Center. Rodney Harrison shares a story about the most he's ever gotten fined. And Nick Wright calls in to talk about Steph Curry and the Warriors fresh off their win in Brooklyn.
